info.title: IBM Cognos TM1 Server, OData Compliant, RESTful API
info.description: This is a swagger.json representation of TM1's RESTful API describing all the available types and root set of paths. The set of paths made available here are those advertised in the service document, those leading to contained properties and function and actions that can be applied, grouped by the type they return.

LocaleID.description: The ID of the locale. To use the default locale, specify 'Default'.

Attributes.description: A set of attributes for the locale.

RLocks.description: A shared lock that allows many threads to read from an object at the same time, but does not allow another thread to modify or write to this object until all R-locks have been released.

IXLocks.description: A lock that reserves the right for a thread to obtain a W-lock on an object when all R-locks have been released.

WLocks.description: An exclusive lock that allows only one thread at a time to access and write changes to an object.

WaitTime.description: The wait time (delay) before a thread should start the process.
